<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" data-theme="gym-light">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GymHelper - 회원가입</title>
    <%- include("partials/themeHeadScript") %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/app.css">
</head>
<body class="auth-bg">
    <div class="relative isolate flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center overflow-hidden p-4 sm:p-6">
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_12%_15%,color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-primary)_16%,transparent)_0%,transparent_42%),radial-gradient(circle_at_90%_0%,color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-secondary)_14%,transparent)_0%,transparent_44%)]"></div>

        <div class="absolute right-4 top-4 z-10 sm:right-6 sm:top-6">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm border border-base-300 bg-base-100/85 backdrop-blur" data-theme-toggle>
                <span class="text-xs">테마</span>
                <span data-theme-label class="badge badge-ghost badge-sm">다크</span>
            </button>
        </div>

        <section class="auth-panel card w-full max-w-[980px] overflow-hidden border border-base-300 bg-base-100/90 shadow-2xl">
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.92fr)_minmax(0,1.08fr)]">
                <aside class="hidden border-r border-base-300/70 bg-base-200/35 p-8 lg:flex lg:flex-col lg:justify-between">
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-primary">GymHelper</p>
                        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight">새 계정을 만들고<br>루틴 기록을 시작하세요</h1>
                        <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">간단한 정보 입력만으로 대시보드와 커뮤니티 기능을 바로 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>
                    </div>

                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-base-content/80">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary"></span>ID: 영문/숫자 5~20자</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary"></span>닉네임은 언제든 변경 가능</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary"></span>가입 후 즉시 로그인 가능</li>
                    </ul>
                </aside>

                <div class="card-body gap-5 p-6 sm:p-8">
                    <div class="space-y-2 text-center lg:text-left">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary lg:hidden">GymHelper</p>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">회원가입</h2>
                        <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">기본 정보를 입력하고 계정을 생성하세요.</p>
                    </div>

                    <form class="signup-form space-y-3" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); signUp();">
                        <label class="form-control w-full">
                            <span class="label-text pb-1 text-sm font-medium">아이디</span>
                            <input type="text" id="id" name="id" required maxlength="20" placeholder="영문/숫자만 입력 가능" class="input input-bordered w-full">
                        </label>

                        <label class="form-control w-full">
                            <span class="label-text pb-1 text-sm font-medium">닉네임</span>
                            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder="닉네임" required class="input input-bordered w-full">
                        </label>

                        <label class="form-control w-full">
                            <span class="label-text pb-1 text-sm font-medium">비밀번호</span>
                            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호" required class="input input-bordered w-full">
                        </label>

                        <label class="form-control w-full">
                            <span class="label-text pb-1 text-sm font-medium">비밀번호 확인</span>
                            <input type="password" id="checkedPassword" name="checkedPassword" placeholder="비밀번호 확인" required class="input input-bordered w-full">
                        </label>

                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mt-2 w-full">회원가입</button>
                    </form>

                    <div class="divider my-0">또는</div>

                    <a href="/logIn" class="btn btn-ghost w-full">이미 계정이 있나요? 로그인</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <script src="/javascripts/theme.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/feedback.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/apiClient.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/signUp.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
